\id 2TH - Fore NT [for] -Papua New Guinea 1974 (web version -2013)
\h 2 Tesaronaika
\toc1 Tesaronaika Kina'mi Nkisa Poro Kaentiye (Tara Yagane)
\toc2 2 Tesaronaika
\toc3 2Te
\mt1 TESARONAIKA KINA'MI NKISA PORO KAENTIYE (TARA YAGANE)
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Poronawa, Sairasiwa, Timotiwa, sumagita esa kaeyune. Tesaronaika kumata monota ai'aru pe kina, tabarempa Koti, Wa'ega Isu Karaisiti, isigeti atokaenta kina, tigeti ma nkisapa kaeyune.
\p 
\v 2 Tabarempa Kotige, Wa'ega Isu Karaisitige, isigetisa awagaenabe paruyenabe tigeti waima waiyeno.
\s1 Poro Kotipa a'mu potantiye
\p 
\v 3 Tao'mitaba, taeba tigeka a'ya'ma yaga Kotiti ta'mu potaompepa, pipa kanarane. A'yugu kampa piyaba pukune. Timatiti'enamaba ampa anosama esegi pegiri, a'ya'ma ka kapa agu kao'enaripa tiyo'mipa puwaitagana, anosagi agama ta'mu potaune.
\v 4 We, tigepa karana puritagiri tiki nakiyenabi mima, kuntaenaba aesaga'ma miyegana, timatiti'enamaba esegi piye. Pika Koti nkaegaranta kina'mi nkaruyenabi tigeri maete iyune.
\s1 Koti antota kamanane
\p 
\v 5 Pigoya, tigeba pintana pekaba, Koti arupu antota'enawapa aborawaekenamana puma tayakiye. Piya, Koti kabiratakena kumata ampikibeka, tige tigupa ago yokege puta waye. Pi kabiratakenaenaraka tiki nakiyenaba aesagabewe.
\v 6 Pigoya, tiki nakiyena purita kina'mipa Kotiba kanara antota iki nakiyenaba aborawaimikiye.
\v 7 Piya aborawaimimagina, tiki nakiyena maeya kina tigepe taepe kaga maeragasima migarakenaenaba tamikiye. Pi ntagaba Wa'ega Isu esegi enisore kina'wantaga, tabe yaku nkabu e'wasaenayaga, tumpa aboramagina,
\v 8 Kotika kampa ibuma, Isu Wa'egarempa nkaogi mono kamana'wa kampa wasiye kina, igepa kamparaga ika antota meru imikiye.
\v 9 Piya, pi ntagaba igeba Koti nkantota'enaba maeyigina kaiwaitakini, Wa'egawama nkaowari kampa wanta, esegiyenawampa nke'wasaenaba kampa asu agakibewe.
\v 10 Pi tumikibi ntagaba, Kotiti atokaenta kina'wampiba ae agega'eba asagayuma, a'ya'waema imatiti pota kina'miba aeka tabera i'mu potakibewe. Pabiyama tigeba tae kamanapa abima timatiti puntapa, pabiyama tabera i'mu potakibewe.
\s1 Pi kina'mi esegi piyema Poro nunamu untiye
\p 
\v 11 Taeba pika napima, asi nasi tigeka Kotirempati nunamu maya yune: Tige utaritanti'na aogima aega'ma mimagiri, aogiyena pukena puntiripa, timatiti yuga pigina, Kotirempa, ae'wa nkesegiyenarasa au'wa aborarimenoma, nunamu yune.
\v 12 Pi pukibentanaga, Wa'egare Isu nkagega'e asagayuyekana, aeba pabiyama tigega'eba asagayukiye. Piya puma, Kotirempa Wa'ega Isu Karaisiti, awagaenawaisitasa pabiya puritase.
\c 2
\s1 Mono akayukena yagarama kamanane
\p 
\v 1 Pigoya, tao'mitaba, Wa'egare Isu Karaisiti aborakibi ntaga aege uma aki pukubompeka urimekiri abiyo.
\v 2 Pipa ka'isa kina'mi: Amonta agaune, ukibipera: Aoso taga kamanapa yunema, ukibipera, taeka: Ige esa kaeyaga maeyune, umagina: Wa'ega aborakena yagaba aborawaeyema yigiripa, a-pami puma karu'enaba a-nkiyegaraiyo.
\v 3 Pigoya, ka yagara a-nkuwa ataigina amiyo kamana urimeno. Piya, Wa'egawama kana'wapa arosakena pekana, mono akayuma akabitakena yagarama maru aborakiye. Piya, a'abibinti tumikena yagara ae maru aborama nagarikiye.
\v 4 Piya, wasanami kotiwaipe aegarantanawaipe kamaena potama a'ya'waemaenaba agisabi kasima, aewa nkagega'e asagayuma, Koti mpono namapi asu pai'ma mara'mima kamana uma aborama: Naeba Kotinawe, piya ukiye.
\p 
\v 5 Napiyenari ago kasapera aya pewe. Pintanaga paipa tigege minta ago urimintone.
\v 6 Pi ntagarama ki akunikenaenaba ago abintawe. Piyama, Koti otantemi ntagaba aborakiye.
\v 7 Piya, ibaba kamana akayukenaenamaba kakama mima yoga pegina, toganaba ke'wa akunintemi'naba ae'watakana wakiye.
\v 8 Pigoya, pi ntagaba pi kamana akayukena yagaraba aborakiye. Piya pekana, Wa'ega Isu nkawamupisa aumawampa aegumagina, pi ntaga ae tumpa aborakibi nkesegiyenawampa agora pubasana kaikiye.
\v 9 Pigoya, kamana akayukena yagara aeba Satani ntugarasa aborakiye. Aborama, uwoma nkesegiyenabe awame'enabe kasa'enabe kumpari'ena aborawaekiye.
\v 10 Piya, ka'isa kina'mi taga kamanakaba kampa ibika, mantari kampa ikibewe. Pigoya, pi ataenabi tumikibi kinapa kana kewama a'ya'ma ata amiyo kamana uwaigasima iyobi airarikaekiye.
\v 11 Piya puma, Koti iyorikaekena ago'ena otakana igeti tumekini, pi kumpari kamanapa aegarakibewe.
\v 12 Piya, taga kamana kampa aega'ma ataenawaimpaka i'mu pe kina, pi a'ya'ma kinapa ata ika maekibewe.
\s1 Kotiba tibabikena uritantiye
\p 
\v 13 We, tao'mitaba, Wa'egawama tigekaba abugaye. Taeba tigeka a'ya'ma yaga Kotiti ta'mu potaompepa, pipa kanarane. Piya, Kotiba ti'ikenagaba paitaka'ya utaritaogana, Aota Awamusa'ama tibabuma Kotiti aota titaogiri, taga kamana aegarantawe. Pintanaraka Koti tibabegi ta'mu puritaune.
\v 14 Pintanaraka Koti abogana, Wa'egare Isu Karaisiti nke'wasaena maekenaga, aogi urimompe mono kamanatasa utaritaogiri aegarantawe.
\v 15 Pigoya, tao'mitaba, esegima asima mima, taga kamana tawamupisabe esapisabe urimintompepa araku'ma aegaraiyo.
\p 
\v 16 Pigoya, Wa'egare Isu Karaisiti aewape tabarempa Kotibe esegi puritaiso. Piya, aeba agu kao'ena puratama, tagu taumapa esegi puratayaba mima, aeti atokaekenaenaga napiyokana awagaenawatasa aogima tao'maeye.
\v 17 Piya, aeba tigupa maema esegi puritama, a'ya'ma aogi kamanape aogiyenabe tonkiya tiyo'maeyano.
\c 3
\s1 Kotiti nunamu otaigina tao'maeyano untiye
\p 
\v 1 We, tao'mitaba, to ka kamanapa waintiye. Abiyo. Taeka nunamu yigina, tigeti aboraompesa puma Wa'egawama kamana'ama uwaesama au'wapa aborano.
\v 2 Piya, nunamu yigina, kampa aogima napinta aguntaena pe kina'mi nkiyapisa ipatatano. Tigeba ago agantawe. Uwoma kina'mi Kotitiba taga imatitiba kampa pewe.
\p 
\v 3 Pigoya, Wa'egawamaba tagantanamana piye. Aeba esegi puritama kabiritakana, aguntaena pemi ntagaramaba kampa tibaebukiye.
\v 4 Piya, Wa'egawama napiyena tamegi, tigekaba mayama napima abune: A'ya'maena piyoma yompentana kanara pewe. Piya, aintiba pabiya pukibekaba, ago abune.
\p 
\v 5 Pigoya, tae tabemika, Wa'egawama tigutipa maema arupu puma, Koti nkagu kao'enawapipe Karaisiti kunta aesaga'ma esegiyenawapipe uwaesaiyo.
\s1 A'ya'ma kinaka yoga kamana waintiye
\p 
\v 6 Pigoya, tao'mitaba, Wa'egare Isu Karaisiti ae awamuta urimekiri aogima abiyo. Ka'waina aeba yogaga aekita puma uwa miyaba yagarama, esegima urimintompe kamana kampa aegaranta uwa miyekiripa, ae'wataiyo.
\v 7 Tigeripa ago abintawe. Tae pompentanaba aegaraiyo. Paipa tigege mintantompepa, yogaga kampa taekita puma mintantompene.
\v 8 Piya, taeba tiyapisa ka'isa nakenaba kampa uwaba maema nantompene. Tige kuntaena puritasanaga arape asekape esegima araga ntuga puyaba mima, ikantanaretasa maema nantompene.
\v 9 Piya, taeba tigetisa naninta uwa maeyompesinta kanara pesine. Pipa kampaye. Taeba tae'enaena aegaraiyoma tayapisa puma tiyakune.
\v 10 Paipa tigege mintapa kamana mayama esegima urimuwakiri, ago abintawe: Yoga kampa pukibi'naba i'miyenoma, urimintompene.
\p 
\v 11 Piyamaba, tigetisa kamana mayama kanagi abune: Ka'isa kina'mi yogawai iyekita puma atate uwa mima, kamana kiki uta nasepa, abune.
\v 12 Pigoya, piya kina'mika, Wa'ega Isu Karaisiti nkawamuta mayama esegima urimigiri abibebe piyo: Pasema mima yogari pumagiri, tigeti ntugarasa nakenaripa maeyiyo.
\p 
\v 13 Piya, tao'mitaba, iyo'maekena yugaba tiyekitaba a-puma uwa piyo.
\v 14 Pigoya, ma nkisapi kaemaraompe kamanapa ka'waina kampa aegarakibipa, ae agoba aogima agamagiri, aegeba a-mpima abira ataigina mima, pika ani peno.
\v 15 Piya, pukibemika kamaena a-potaiyo. Pipa kampaye. Tiyo'ena puma arupu napiyena amiyo.
\s1 To ka'isa kamanane
\p 
\v 16 Wa'ega, aeba paruyenama nkagowama, a'ya'waemaenabi miyigina asi nasi aewa paruyena aborarimeno. Piya, pi Wa'egaba a'ya'ma kina'mititi miyeno.
\p 
\v 17 Naeba Poronawe. Naeba: Aya pewema, nae'ne ntayapisa kaeyuwe. Piya, a'ya'ma isa'nempa ara'enane kaeyuwa, agama naepisa aogima abiyo.
\p 
\v 18 Pigoya, Wa'egare Isu Karaisiti nkawagaenawampaba a'ya'ma tigeti waima waiyeno.
\q1 Poro piya isa kaentiye. 
